title: DoctorStory2
tags:
position: 169,38
---
Doctor Ghost: You know, it always amazes me how much someone's life can change through someone else's actions.
Doctor Ghost: As a doctor, I've treated so many patients. Some of them were old, barely hanging on to life but still fighting to stay with their loved ones as long as possible.
Doctor Ghost: Others were young, hurt by things out of their control. People of all ages and backgrounds all come to the hospital for the same purpose, for another chance at life.
Doctor Ghost: Whenever I see their smile or the smile of their loved ones, I realize how much I changed their lives.
Doctor Ghost: When I was young, I never could have imagined what direction my life would go. But it was all thanks to a stranger that I became who I am today.
Doctor Ghost: I hope I can find them one day so I can thank them.
<<setCam "Main Camera">>
===

title: DoctorStory3
tags:
position: 169,38
---
Doctor Ghost: Hey... Have you seen... Never mind.
Doctor Ghost: This shouldn't be something I should bother you with. If you wish to know, however, I'm looking for a certain soldier.
Doctor Ghost: He was the stranger I mentioned last time. I heard from some other ghosts that he might have been seen here.
Doctor Ghost: I... I have to find him.
Doctor Ghost: He was the reason why I lived to be a doctor.
Doctor Ghost: Why I... even got a chance live in the first place.
Doctor Ghost: I had an illness when I was young. And because our village didn't have a doctor, I was certain I was going to die.
Doctor Ghost: But when our village was attacked by some enemies, that soldier saved me
Doctor Ghost: I didn't want his sacrifice to be in vain, so I pushed myself to live.
Doctor Ghost: When relief came and the doctors there cured me, I dedicated myself to become a doctor as well.
<<setCam "Main Camera">>
